# Prize delivery jurney


I will try to conceptualize in this document what happens after the trigger raffle mechanism happens for a succesfull raffle. 


## Prerequisites:
- A raffle was triggered succesfully
- The winner ticket was selected
- All the statuses are properly set on raffle and tickets for that raffle
- The raffle creator is notified that the raffle is succesfull and he has to wait for the ticket winner to priovide it's shipping details
- The users who have a looser ticket will be notified that the  ticket's they owned lost in that raffle
- The user how owns the winner ticket (even though he might have other tickets that are lost tickets) will be notified with a message that he has
won the Raffle and he needs to provide his shipping details for the raffle so the Raffle owner can send him the prize.

## Details

I need to model this situation and I am thinking to create a PrizeDelivery entity and a PrizeDeliveryLog(for better tracing)
At this point both entities will be created - they need references to the raffle, user and the ticket

